🚢 Task 02: Titanic Dataset Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

# Objective

Cleaned a raw passenger dataset by handling missing values (imputing age and embarked values while dropping cabin/deck data) and built a visual dashboard to analyze how gender, passenger class, and family size correlated with survival rates.

# Tools Used

* Pandas
* Matplotlib
* Seaborn

# Status ✅ Completed


🌳 Task 03: Decision Tree Classifier for Customer Purchase Prediction

# Objective

Built a machine learning Decision Tree Classifier to predict whether a customer would purchase a product or service based on demographic and behavioral banking data.

# Tools Used

* Scikit-Learn
* Pandas
* Matplotlib

